-- McEwen Hired by Title Insurer Group for Federal Lobbying Post
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2011-12-20T20:12:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-20/mcewen-hired-by-title-insurer-group-for-federal-lobbying-post.html
Jessica McEwen was hired as director
of government affairs for the group representing U.S. title
insurers.  McEwen, previously a legislative assistant to
Representative Joe Donnelly and advised the Indiana Democrat on
the Dodd-Frank Act, will be responsible for federal lobbying,
the  American Land Title Association  said today in a statement
distributed by  Business Wire .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in  New York  at 
 nbuhayar@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  